    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Adhi Kartiko Pratama Tbk operates as a nickel ore mining company in Indonesia. It offers sea port services, including the operation of terminal facilities, such as ports and docks, navigation, cargo inspection, shipping and docking services, mooring services, and guidance and delay services for water transportation of passengers, animals, or goods; industrial estate services, which include the land operation for centralized industrial activities; and analytical and technical testing services, such as operations related to laboratory safety and security, and technical testing involving ionizing radiation sources, as well as the implementation of proficiency testing and the production of reference materials. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Kendari, Indonesia. PT Adhi Kartiko Pratama Tbk is a subsidiary of PT. Energy Battery Indonesia.",
